Package camp

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    ICheckCampVisibility
    Represents an interface to check within a camp database if a camp is visible.
    ICheckNoClash
    Represents an interface to check within a camp database, if a specific camp has clashing ongoing dates with a list of other camps within the database.
    ICheckRegistrationClosed
    Represents an interface to check within a camp database if a camp's registration date has passed.
    ICheckSchoolMatch
    Represents an interface to check within a camp database if a camp is indeed open to a student's faculty.
    ICreateCamp
    Represents an interface to create a camp within a camp database.
    IDeleteCamp
    Represents an interface to delete a camp within a camp database.
    IEditCamp
    Represents an interface to edit the details of a camp within a camp database.
    IFilterCamps
    Represents an interface to set the filter bits of all camps within a camp database based on the filter string.
    IGeneratePerformanceReport
    Represents an interface to generate a performance report of the camp committee members of the camps that the staff is in charge of.
    IGenerateStudentReport
    Represents an interface to generate a camp report.
    IGetCampsCreated
    Represents an interface to check and return the list of camps that a staff created, within a camp database.
    IGetCampSlots
    Represents an interface to obtain the remaining number of camp slots.
    IIncreaseCampSlots
    Represents an interface to increase the remaining number of camp slots of a camp in a database.
    IPrintRegisteredCamps
    Represents an interface that prints all the camp details and corresponding roles of a student, given his list of camps registered and his respective roles.
    IReduceCampSlots
    Represents an interface to reduce the remaining number of camp slots of a camp in a database.
    ISortCamps
    Represents an interface to sort all camps in a camp database according to some order defined by the implementor class.
    IViewAllCamps
    Represents an interface to view all camps that a user is allowed to see in a camp database.
    IViewOwnCamps
    Represents an interface to view all camps from a camp database that a user is in charge of.
